CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 22, 1964, pg. 6 reads: Mr. and Mrs. Clifton Victor Simmons - Harris Photo...Miss Barbara Jean Smith and Clifton Victor Simmons were married in a fashionable double ring rites at Ebenezer Baptist Church."
TitMainTitle: Wedding party including bridesmaids Yvonne Turentine, Barbara Dunn, Patricia Chavis, Marian Coon, Janet Munday, and Lois Jones; Best man and ushers including Donald Jones, Edward Tibbs, Nathaniel Dunn, Ralph Young, and William Pryor; groom Clifton Victor Simmons and bride Barbara Jean Smith Simmons in center, flower girl Jeanie Wells and ring bearer George Young, posed on stage underneath crepe paper streamers in basement of Ebenezer Baptist church
